A state engage in carry some state
==================================
Every human being move in their life having some up and down feeling/energy. Some time it many be much up and some time it may be much down.
We get awareness about little up and little down since it come in our life daily/weekly/monthly. But some time our feeling/stress/happiness break the threshold/limit
and we keep this in our memory as spot(black/white).
We try to forget the black and and try to remember the white on surface of mind since it seems to be gives the energy, if we don't have sufficient energy at some moment then our senses automatically try to fined energy near about ie. it try to generate some hopes and if is not find some hope then try to fly in white sport that it kept in storage.

This is nothing but state who carry the previous state,but in fact we can't carry any state, the state always exists in that time only when it get streaming. We carry the image of that state because we realize there is some energy rest there, It also seems to be carry the experience but in fact it not we who carry the experience it the energy who get cross the state and realization get injected into the energy.

Ex-
-When we eat something(apple) whatever the energy get by body instantly that energy get carry by body automatically and it is we who carry the test of that food.
The time we eat apple at that time only all the energy get by body there is no any meaning to carry the eating state later. We can imagine the state of eating apple but the same state can't be carry. Only the energy get body can be carry and that is automatically no need to any thing for that.

-When we support some one whatever energy get instantly that automatically get carry but whatever test get absorbed that carry by us.

Carry int the external state
--------------------------------
From where we get energy first time our senses/mind point to that resource and expect more and more energy due carry the first sate of gating energy only, but it unable
to understand there is no any external source exists who doing the production of energy simply for them. What ever energy we get form external source the exactly the same amount of energy we send back to them by some media, it is in observation or not doesn't matter.

Here mind/our poor understanding always take lead to carry the white state for further since it always is in lack of energy.

Ex-
It is obvious, if we are in always hungry state and if you get some food from some source then automatically our attention always move towards that direction.but
If we are able to produce/arrange food by self then not need to look towards the external source for food.

Carry the intern state
--------------------------
When we supply energy continuously then whatever the next state come that is more energetic and light so there is no any meaning to carry the previous state of feeling.

Ex-
Today you get burned bread, next day you get bread, next day you get bread and vegetable, next day you get bread,rice,pulse,vegetable, next day you get fruits.so on
then it is obvious you not carry the previous state of food, you may look the previous state of food to know how our food gating changed day by day but you never greed for previous state of food.

But when you not supply continuous energy then it may be possible to call the previous state and this is due to lack of energy, this is similar to external greed.

***Any State can't be carry by another state***
***State is already bundle of time/streaming***
